<body style="background: #1a1a2e; color: #eee; font-family: monospace; padding: 20px;">
  <h1>üîç Pitch Deck Diagnostic Page</h1>

  <div style="background: #16213e; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
