    <p style="color: #0f3; font-size: 20px;">‚úÖ If you can see this, Astro is serving pages correctly</p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #16213e; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h2>Test 2: Check Main Pitch Deck</h2>
    <p>Go to: <a href="/pitch" style="color: #00d4ff;">/pitch</a></p>
    <p>Then press F12 and check Console tab for errors</p>
